### Observability Playground – REST API Collection
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client, JetBrains HTTP Client, curl
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@mimir    = http://localhost:9009
@loki     = http://localhost:3100
@tempo    = http://localhost:3200
@grafana  = http://localhost:3000
@oncall   = http://localhost:8080
@app      = http://localhost:8000
@otel     = http://localhost:4320
@minio    = http://localhost:9001
@gf_user  = admin
@gf_pass  = admin123


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  MIMIR – Prometheus-compatible Metrics API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health / readiness
GET {{mimir}}/ready

### List all metric names
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/label/__name__/values

### List all label names
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/labels

### Instant query – count all active series
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query?query=count({__name__!=""})

### Instant query – HTTP request rate
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query?query=rate(http_requests_total[5m])

### Instant query – service error rate
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query?query=sum by (service) (rate(http_requests_total{status=~"5.."}[5m]))

### Instant query – p99 latency
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query?query=histogram_quantile(0.99, rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))

### Range query – request rate over last hour
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query_range?query=rate(http_requests_total[5m])&start=-1h&end=now&step=1m

### Metric metadata
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/metadata

### Series for a specific metric
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/series?match[]=http_requests_total

### Label values for a label
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/label/service/values

### Top-50 metrics by series count
GET {{mimir}}/prometheus/api/v1/query?query=topk(50, count by (__name__) ({__name__!=""}))

### Remote write (push metrics directly)
POST {{mimir}}/api/v1/push
Content-Type: application/x-protobuf


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  LOKI – Log Aggregation API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health
GET {{loki}}/ready

### List all log labels
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/labels

### Label values for a specific label
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/label/service_name/values

### Query last 100 log lines
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/query_range?query={job!=""}&limit=100&direction=backward

### Query logs for a service
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/query_range?query={service_name="sample-app"}&limit=100

### Filter logs containing "error"
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/query_range?query={service_name="sample-app"} |= "error"&limit=50

### LogQL metric – log rate per service
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/query_range?query=sum by (service_name) (rate({service_name!=""}[5m]))&step=1m

### Push logs to Loki
POST {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/push
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "streams": [
    {
      "stream": { "service_name": "test", "level": "info", "job": "manual-push" },
      "values": [
        ["{{$timestamp}}", "Hello from the API collection!"]
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Loki index stats
GET {{loki}}/loki/api/v1/index/stats?query={service_name!=""}&start=-1h&end=now


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  TEMPO – Distributed Tracing API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health
GET {{tempo}}/ready

### Search traces (last 30 min)
GET {{tempo}}/api/search?limit=20

### Search traces by service
GET {{tempo}}/api/search?tags=service.name=sample-app&limit=20

### Search traces by operation
GET {{tempo}}/api/search?tags=name=create_order&limit=10

### Search traces with min duration (>100ms)
GET {{tempo}}/api/search?minDuration=100ms&limit=20

### Get a specific trace by ID (replace TRACE_ID)
GET {{tempo}}/api/traces/TRACE_ID_HERE

### TraceQL query
GET {{tempo}}/api/search?q={.service.name="sample-app"}

### Tempo metrics
GET {{tempo}}/metrics


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  GRAFANA – Dashboard & Alerting API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Grafana health
GET {{grafana}}/api/health
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

### List all dashboards
GET {{grafana}}/api/search?type=dash-db&limit=100
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

### List datasources
GET {{grafana}}/api/datasources
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

### List alert rules
GET {{grafana}}/api/ruler/grafana/api/v1/rules
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

### Create a folder
POST {{grafana}}/api/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

{
  "title": "Observability Playground"
}

### Grafana annotations – list
GET {{grafana}}/api/annotations
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

### Create an annotation
POST {{grafana}}/api/annotations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}

{
  "text": "Deploy v1.0.0",
  "tags": ["deploy", "production"]
}

### Grafana users
GET {{grafana}}/api/users
Authorization: Basic {{gf_user}}:{{gf_pass}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  GRAFANA ONCALL – Incident Management API
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### OnCall health
GET {{oncall}}/health/

### List integrations
GET {{oncall}}/api/v1/integrations/
Authorization: Token YOUR_ONCALL_TOKEN_HERE

### List alert groups (incidents)
GET {{oncall}}/api/v1/alert_groups/
Authorization: Token YOUR_ONCALL_TOKEN_HERE

### List on-call schedules
GET {{oncall}}/api/v1/schedules/
Authorization: Token YOUR_ONCALL_TOKEN_HERE

### Create test alert (replace INTEGRATION_TOKEN)
POST {{oncall}}/integrations/v1/INTEGRATION_TOKEN/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Alert from API Collection",
  "message": "This is a test alert",
  "severity": "warning"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  SAMPLE APP – OTel-instrumented service
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health
GET {{app}}/api/health

### App info (OTel endpoint, version)
GET {{app}}/api/info

### List products
GET {{app}}/api/products

### Get single product
GET {{app}}/api/products/p001

### Create order (generates trace + metrics + logs)
POST {{app}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "p002",
  "quantity": 3,
  "region": "us-east"
}

### List users
GET {{app}}/api/users

### Simulate error (5xx)
GET {{app}}/api/simulate/error

### Simulate slow request
GET {{app}}/api/simulate/slow?delay=2.0

### Simulate load burst
GET {{app}}/api/simulate/load?requests=20

### Prometheus metrics scrape
GET {{app}}/metrics


